author: kmarsden
msg: The test intentionally does not close ResultSets to test for a leak, but this
was causing an error dropping the table. Changed the test to close the last ResultSet and gc() to avoid the drop table error.

author: bimargulies
msg: MtoM is specified as an optimization. This change allows the DataHandler
binding to work, somewhat, when mtom is turned off, rather than going ahead
and creating attachments even when it has been sternly instructed not to do so.
